snippet.title: "Aquaman" stars Jason Momoa, Amber Heard at Director James Wan, nasa Pilipinas
snippet.description:
#ChikaMinute: Nasa bansa ngayon ang mga bida at direktor ng pelikulang "Aquaman" sa pangunguna ni Jason Momoa. Nagkuwento rin sila sa challenges na pinagdaanan nila sa paggawa ng pelikula. Maki-chika tayo kay Nelson Canlas. 

24 Oras is GMA Network’s flagship newscast, anchored by Mike Enriquez, Mel Tiangco and Vicky Morales. It airs on GMA-7 Mondays to Fridays at 6:30 PM (PHL Time) and on weekends at 5:30 PM. For more videos from 24 Oras, visit http://www.gmanetwork.com/24oras.
